text: Yes, it's hard to believe but they've got really good 北京炸酱面 and this "青椒面" was really good too.. love the texture of the noodles and the flavor is not those fiery 四川 type.. with that said, it was enhanced by adding some Chinese chilli/ oil. This might become a 必点 each time we're here.

very good noodles and dumplings.

try the cold noodles! awesome texture and spice
This is the second time I visit this store. The 炸酱面 here is authentic. Made me miss Beijing so much. Love it. Will be back for more.
The noodles are delicious! The skin jelly is also recommended!
